             was indicted for <rs id="t18011202-38-off197" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18011202-38-off197" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18011202-38-off197" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18011202-38-cd198" type="crimeDate">7th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011202-38-off197 t18011202-38-cd198"></join>, fifty-six yards of calico, value 46s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18011202-38-victim366" type="victimName">
                        Jonathan 
                        Watson
                     <interp inst="t18011202-38-victim366" type="surname" value="Watson"></interp>
